24 February 2012Members of the media are invited to the post State of the Nation Address (SoNA) media briefing of the International Cooperation Trade and Security (ICTS) cluster. The Chairperson of the cluster, Minister of Defence and Military Veterans, Lindiwe Sisulu will lead the briefing. The details are as follows: Date: Sunday, 26 February 2012 Time: 10h00 Venue: Imbizo Media Centre in Parliament, Cape Town NB: There will be a video-link to GCIS Auditorium, 1st Floor, Midtown Building, Pretoria Kindly confirm attendance by email or sms to: Professor Ndawonde (Pretoria) Cell: 078 456 5738 E-mail: proffesor@gcis.gov.za Mzimasi Ngqelu (Cape Town) Cell: 076 904 3557 E-mail: mzi@gcis.gov.za Enquiries: Mzobanzi Jikazana (Pretoria) Cell: 083 641 2355 Liezil Cerf (Cape Town) Cell: 076 778 2380 Issued by: Government Communication and Information System